OL,3,CWales' universities 'in crisis',
OL,4,Cunions warn
OL,6,FWales' universities are in "crisis"
OL,7,Fand risk being brought "to their
OL,8,Fknees' - the warnings of two unions
OL,9,Fworking in the sector.
OL,11,FThere has been a series of job losses
OL,12,Fand course closures announced in
OL,13,Frecent months as higher education
OL,14,Finstitutions try to deal with a
OL,15,Ffunding shortfall and mounting debts.
OL,17,FRepresentatives of Unison and the
OL,18,FUniversities and College Union (UCU)
OL,19,Fhave been giving evidence to the
OL,20,FSenedd's Children, Young People and
OL,21,FEducation Committee today (Wednesday.)
