OL,3,CWales' universities 'in crisis',
OL,4,Cunions warn
OL,6,FIn its written evidence, Unison -
OL,7,Fwhich represents support staff - wrote
OL,8,Fthat, "Welsh universities are in
OL,9,Fcrisis. Hundreds of job losses are
OL,10,Fexpected with a catastrophic effect on
OL,11,Fstaff, institutions, students,
OL,12,Fcommunities and the Welsh economy.
OL,14,F"It's dishonest for universities to
OL,15,Ftalk about enhancing the student
OL,16,Fexperience when this is significantly
OL,17,Fundermined by the scale of job cuts.
