OL,3,CWales' universities 'in crisis',
OL,4,Cunions warn
OL,6,F"There's an urgent need for Welsh
OL,7,Fgovernment to decide what it wants the
OL,8,FHE sector to deliver and for this to
OL,9,Fbe properly funded. It must produce a
OL,10,Fdetailed industrial strategy which
OL,11,Foutlines the skills and number of
OL,12,Fgraduates Wales requires for the
OL,13,Ffuture across a range of jobs and
OL,14,Fensure universities have the capacity
OL,15,Fto train these young people."
