OL,3,CWales' universities 'in crisis',
OL,4,Cunions warn
OL,6,FMeanwhile, UCU, which speaks for
OL,7,Facademic staff, wrote that "UCU Cymru
OL,8,Fnotes that Higher Education has
OL,9,Fsuffered systematic failure and
OL,10,Fneglect which, combined with the
OL,11,Frecent hike in operating costs, risks
OL,12,Fbringing many Welsh institutions to
OL,13,Ftheir knees."
OL,15,FDuring the committee meeting Gareth
OL,16,FLloyd of UCU said "The danger is, if
OL,17,Fwe're not careful, this is going to
OL,18,Fhave a really detrimental effect on
OL,19,Fstudents who don't want to go there.
OL,20,FAnd that really, really worries me."
