OL,3,CWales' universities 'in crisis',
OL,4,Cunions warn
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales after the
OL,7,Fmeeting, Dan Beard of Unison, said
OL,8,Fthat he fears that the job losses
OL,9,Fwon't solve the problem and could make
OL,10,Fit far worse. He said that, "My worry
OL,11,Fis we're going to see a real reduction
OL,12,Fin capacity and more job losses,
OL,13,Fperhaps even the collapse of certain
OL,14,Funiversities."
